{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7584c3ed6a","title":"内江专区农村人口非正常死亡不少","origin":"美国图书馆收藏","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"77fdcb6bf8","index":0,"year":1956,"month":6,"day":2,"articleId":"7584c3ed6a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"609473e888","name":"李朝"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4836d7c193","type":"title","text":"内江专区农村人口非正常死亡不少","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"7584c3ed6a"},{"id":"90f1867fa5","type":"authors","text":"李朝","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"7584c3ed6a"},{"id":"60259e0ff5","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社成都2日讯：内江专区各县从1月到4月8日，共发生非正常死亡事件三零三起，其中自杀、被杀事件二一二起，意外死亡九十一起，另1月到5月6日，还有五十六个小孩被水淹死、被火烧死、跌死。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"7584c3ed6a"},{"id":"c1b8c3ab3d","type":"paragraph","text":"据分析：发生非正常死亡的主要原因是：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"7584c3ed6a"},{"id":"74f053b0bc","type":"paragraph","text":"1·不少地区为了完成兴修水利等基本建设任务，忽视安全生产。全区因忽视安全，淹互、跌死、被岩石或土墙倒塌压死等死亡的就有九十一起。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"7584c3ed6a"},{"id":"3ed6c496b6","type":"paragraph","text":"2·干部忽视对贫苦社员和老弱残废者的救济问题。部分老弱者以为“办了高级社，老年人没前途了”因此，从3月22日到5月2日，就发生五起老弱者自杀的事件。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"7584c3ed6a"},{"id":"20fcbcf7e3","type":"paragraph","text":"3·因婚姻问题夫妇纠纷、群众纠纷自杀的也较多。（李朝）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"7584c3ed6a"},{"id":"4e7b97010d","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：根据1956年6月2日新华社《内部参考》。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"7584c3ed6a"}],"page":{"id":"97808bcada","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"7584c3ed6a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}